PrecisAmendments to Order in Council P.C. 1986-1/2914 of December 18, 1986, as amended, which extend the duration of the FARM DEBT REVIEW PROGRAM (whereby payments are made to the Farm Credit Corporation on behalf of farmers who are in financial difficulty) for a further period of one year, that is until March 31, 1993, and revise certain conditions concerning proportional concessions.
